parameters:
【Masamune】 A key, huh? Looks like this can open
the door.
【Tommy】 Maybe someone also made this dungeon.
【Masamune】 I see.
【Masamune】 Hmm, something has fallen.
【Masamune】 Is this... a record stone?

【Leon】 I wonder what kind of record is inside.
Let's take a look.

【Masamune】 Can I just look at it without
permission?

【Skeleton Head】 Hey, don't just press the dungeon
switch so easily.

【Skeleton Head】 There might be a possibility of
traps.
【Masamune】 Is that so?

【Skeleton Head】 That's right... That's why...
Ahh...
【Masamune】 What's wrong!
【Skeleton Head】 My crotch is tingling... Uwaaahhh
【Masamune】 Skeleton Head!
【Masamune】 ...

【Skeleton Head】 Haa, haa... It's a forced
ejaculation magic... That's why I told you to be
careful.

【Masamune】 (Of all people, Skeleton Head... I
wanted to see Tommy's instead)
【Skeleton Head】 Hey, are you listening?
A
A
